sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant VS as Istio VirtualService
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Agent as Agent Sidecar<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelServer as Model Server Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant EventSink as Event Sink<br/>80/443 HTTP/HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Model Deployment & Loading

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>VS: TLS Termination

    Note over ModelServer,S3: Init Container runs first
    ModelServer->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>AWS IAM/Secret Key
    S3-->>ModelServer: Model files
    Note over ModelServer: storage-initializer copies to /mnt/models

    Note over Client,EventSink: Flow 2: Inference Request (Serverless)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    Gateway->>VS: Route to InferenceService
    VS->>Activator: Forward request<br/>HTTP mTLS<br/>Client cert

    alt Pod scaled to zero
        Activator->>ModelServer: Scale up pod
        Note over ModelServer: Pod starts, loads model from /mnt/models
    end

    Activator->>Agent: Forward to agent sidecar<br/>HTTP localhost
    Agent->>Agent: Batching (if enabled)
    Agent->>ModelServer: Inference request<br/>HTTP :8080
    ModelServer->>ModelServer: Run inference
    ModelServer-->>Agent: Prediction result
    Agent-->>Activator: Response
    Activator-->>VS: Response
    VS-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    opt Request/Response Logging
        Agent->>EventSink: Send CloudEvent<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Bearer Token
    end

    Note over Client,EventSink: Flow 3: Multi-Model InferenceGraph

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/ensemble:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>VS: Route to InferenceGraph
    VS->>Agent: Forward to Router Pod<br/>HTTP mTLS

    par Parallel Model Calls
        Agent->>ModelServer: Call Model A<br/>HTTP mTLS
        ModelServer-->>Agent: Result A
    and
        Agent->>ModelServer: Call Model B<br/>HTTP mTLS
        ModelServer-->>Agent: Result B
    end

    Agent->>Agent: Combine results
    Agent-->>VS: Ensemble response
    VS-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: LLM Distributed Inference

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/llm/infer<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>ModelServer: Route to LeaderWorkerSet Leader<br/>HTTP mTLS

    par Multi-Node Processing
        ModelServer->>ModelServer: Leader Pod (vLLM)<br/>GPU processing
    and
        ModelServer->>ModelServer: Worker Pod 1<br/>Ray cluster<br/>6379/8265 TCP
    and
        ModelServer->>ModelServer: Worker Pod 2<br/>Ray cluster
    end

    ModelServer-->>Gateway: LLM response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response
